WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:07.000
Yes, you are eligible to apply for admission to NYU Abu Dhabi even if you have started working toward an undergraduate degree at another school

00:07.000 --> 00:15.000
However, regardless of the amount or level of coursework already completed, all students will enter NYU Abu Dhabi as first year students for a four-year course of study

00:15.000 --> 00:21.000
At this time, however, we discourage students who have completed two years or more of an undergraduate degree from applying

